posts.post_title: FS/FT: T206s you are looking for
posts.post_content: Hello to all, I am interested in selling or trading....Please let me know what you are looking for including grade range. Also, if you're looking to buy or trade. I did this a while back and alot of cards moved! Thanks.....

I believe a thread was started a week ago for all 206 collectors to post their wantlists.  Perhaps you might find a buyer or trading partner there.  

[url]http://www.net54baseball.com/showthread.php?t=162046[/url]

Best,

Andy
